query.pigql: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'CSAT' >= -10; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "false"; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate percentile_disc(0.25) within group (order by 'CSAT' asc) as 'per_CSAT';

q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'CSAT' >= -10; ENDTOTAL = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "false"; updcreatedTOTAL = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "LastYearCompare").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')")}}; updclosedTOTAL = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('ClosedDate_Year','ClosedDate_Month','ClosedDate_Day')")}};compare = group updcreatedTOTAL by all full, updclosedTOTAL by all full, ENDTOTAL by all; compare = foreach compare generate 100*(avg(updclosedTOTAL.'CSAT')-avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT'))/avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT') as 'perc_Percent', (case when 100*(avg(updclosedTOTAL.'CSAT')-avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT'))/avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT') < 0 then "#ff545f" when 100*(avg(updclosedTOTAL.'CSAT')-avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT'))/avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT') > 0 then "#ee9f77" else "#32b181" end) as 'color';

query.pigql: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'CSAT' <= 34; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "false"; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate count() as count;

q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'CSAT' <= {{coalesce(cell(kpi_bottom_quartile.result, 0, "per_CSAT"),0).asObject()}}; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "false"; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate count() as count;

lens_table.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('ClosedDate_Year','ClosedDate_Month','ClosedDate_Day')")}}; q = foreach q generate 'CaseNumber', first('Account_Name') as 'Account_Name', first('CSAT') as 'CSAT', first('First_Contact_Close__c') as 'First_Contact_Close__c',  first('Type') as 'Type', first('Owner_Name') as 'Owner_Name', first('MilestoneStatus__c') as 'MilestoneStatus__c', avg('{{column(Static_Duration.selection, ["pigql_value"]).asObject()}}') as '{{column(Static_Duration.selection, ["measure_field"]).asObject()}}', first('Origin') as 'Origin', first('Priority') as 'Priority', first('Status') as 'Status', first('Type_of_Support__c') as 'Type_of_Support__c', first('IsEscalated') as 'Escalated' ; q = order q by 'CaseNumber' desc; q = limit q 100;

query.pigql: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'CSAT' >= -10; ENDTOTAL = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "false"; updcreatedTOTAL = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "LastPeriodCompare").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')")}}; updclosedTOTAL = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('ClosedDate_Year','ClosedDate_Month','ClosedDate_Day')")}};compare = group updcreatedTOTAL by all full, updclosedTOTAL by all full, ENDTOTAL by all; compare = foreach compare generate 100*(avg(updclosedTOTAL.'CSAT')-avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT'))/avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT') as 'perc_Percent', (case when 100*(avg(updclosedTOTAL.'CSAT')-avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT'))/avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT') < 0 then "#f2536d" when 100*(avg(updclosedTOTAL.'CSAT')-avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT'))/avg(updcreatedTOTAL.'CSAT') > 0 then "#3CAF6D" else "#32b181" end) as 'color';
